Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我其實並不討厭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽…
